body:
@knurl Thank you for raising this. I can confirm that it returns an exit code of 0 regardless if errors updating repos.

This is because the code in https://github.com/helm/helm/blob/main/cmd/helm/repo_update.go#L117, just outputs any error messages and does not return an error in the the cobra command. Therefore, cobra will return 0 always.

I am unsure if this is as expected or not. I will therefore add it to the Helm  weekly meeting for discussion.
